WEBVTT

01:19.211 --> 01:23.149
Hey. I just, I uh...

01:23.182 --> 01:28.188
it's urgent that you... What?

01:32.625 --> 01:36.863
My love. My wife.

01:40.833 --> 01:43.269
Death that has
sucked the honey of thy breath.

01:43.569 --> 01:47.874
Hath no power yet upon thy
beauty. Thou are not conquered.

02:07.893 --> 02:09.662
What the?

02:16.735 --> 02:18.705
Why are you dressed like that?

02:19.238 --> 02:20.740
Is the play over?

02:22.608 --> 02:25.912
Look, if this is about

02:25.945 --> 02:28.680
what I think it's about,

02:28.714 --> 02:32.418
I haven't
said anything to anyone.

02:38.224 --> 02:40.292
Our little secret, right?

02:47.900 --> 02:51.337
I, I swear. I, I promise.

02:52.738 --> 02:57.710
Juliet?
Why art thou yet so fair?

03:02.615 --> 03:04.717
Damn it!

03:09.588 --> 03:12.492
Shall I believe that
unsubstantial death is amorous?

03:12.825 --> 03:15.628
Keeps thee here in
the dark to be his paramour?

03:18.764 --> 03:19.932
The doors to breath.

03:22.968 --> 03:25.338
No. No, no, no, no.

03:25.371 --> 03:27.373
You, you,
you don't have to do this.

03:27.406 --> 03:29.976
Please. I won't tell a soul.

03:31.910 --> 03:36.781
Help! No! You don't have to
do this. Please. No, no, no, no.

03:37.816 --> 03:39.752
Seal it with a righteous kiss.

04:14.586 --> 04:18.858
♪ OMINOUS SYNTHESIZER ♪

05:12.077 --> 05:15.615
Taylor. Can you hear me?

05:17.616 --> 05:21.486
You've been through quite a
lot young lady. Do you know how

05:21.520 --> 05:25.558
lucky you are? Can you
remember much? Anything at all?

05:30.496 --> 05:32.765
Grace Fisher was a
guidance counselor at Crystal

05:32.798 --> 05:36.102
Lake High. She was brutally
slain last night when an unknown

05:36.135 --> 05:38.938
assailant approached her as
she was leaving for the evening.

05:38.971 --> 05:42.575
Police are urging anybody with
any information to reach out to

05:42.608 --> 05:47.513
Detective Ace Hoffman. Your tips
will remain anonymous. Details

05:47.546 --> 05:49.515
of the wake will be on
this evening's broadcast.

05:49.548 --> 05:51.384
What a loss.

05:52.651 --> 05:55.655
You know I don't like it when
you sneak up on me like that.

05:57.523 --> 06:01.060
I'm sorry about last night.
I don't like when we argue.

06:01.093 --> 06:04.464
Things are really
complicated right now.

06:05.164 --> 06:06.966
Gross. Can you not?

06:06.999 --> 06:09.502
Oh honey,
I, I didn't see you there.

06:09.535 --> 06:12.037
Did you get the
tickets for us for tonight?

06:12.070 --> 06:14.607
Yes, front and center as always.

06:14.640 --> 06:16.509
Don't forget
my cast party's tonight.

06:16.542 --> 06:17.943
Okay, I can come and pick you

06:17.976 --> 06:19.187
up. I mean
if there's gonna be drinking

06:19.211 --> 06:20.651
I just really
want you to be careful.

06:20.679 --> 06:23.416
No, mom I'm fine. Stop.

06:23.449 --> 06:24.850
Hey, here don't forget this.

06:24.883 --> 06:26.051
You ridin' with me today?

06:27.753 --> 06:29.055
I'll walk.

06:29.088 --> 06:31.690
Well, I don't care how
you get there but you better

06:31.723 --> 06:33.526
get going
or you're gonna be late.

06:33.559 --> 06:37.163
♪ CHILL POP MUSIC ♪

06:46.972 --> 06:51.210
♪ The light is
falling with the weight ♪

06:51.243 --> 06:55.481
♪ Like a grudge to bear ♪

06:56.081 --> 07:00.519
♪ It lingers for a while ♪

07:00.552 --> 07:04.757
♪ And when you
hold it you feel brave ♪

07:04.790 --> 07:08.428
♪ Even though you're not ♪

07:08.927 --> 07:13.232
♪ For you are not you ♪

07:13.265 --> 07:18.070
♪ Love is alive in here ♪

07:18.103 --> 07:22.107
♪ In the hands of kings ♪

07:22.140 --> 07:26.111
♪ Who couldn't fight ♪

07:59.811 --> 08:02.048
Hey there Taylor.

08:02.281 --> 08:05.785
Hey. Drew right?

08:07.286 --> 08:09.889
Of course it is,
my dad had the same name.

08:10.622 --> 08:11.824
Had?

08:12.658 --> 08:15.595
Yeah he's, uh,
he's gone. It's a long story.

08:17.229 --> 08:20.566
So uh, how've you been?

08:22.134 --> 08:27.039
Considering? Been better.

08:28.040 --> 08:32.111
Thanks for asking. Real
question is how have you been?

08:32.644 --> 08:35.982
It may not seem like
it but I'm living the dream.

08:37.616 --> 08:39.251
Pretty crazy huh?

08:42.587 --> 08:44.656
I think it's exciting.

08:52.931 --> 08:55.067
Well, it's been
nice talking with you

08:55.100 --> 08:58.737
but uh, I've gotta get back
to work. Toilets won't clean

08:58.770 --> 09:00.039
themselves.

09:12.117 --> 09:13.419
Sorry I'm late.

09:13.452 --> 09:16.989
Class is nearly over. Can't
keep lettin' you off the hook.

09:17.022 --> 09:18.991
It's not fair to
the other students.

09:19.992 --> 09:23.663
The best part of my morning
is spent imagining him naked.

09:24.863 --> 09:27.299
That is so gross
Hannah. He's like 40.

09:27.332 --> 09:30.937
Oh come on Lily. You're telling
me you wouldn't fuck him?

09:31.236 --> 09:35.874
No. He's a teacher. Besides,
he's dating Taylor's mom.

09:35.907 --> 09:37.610
You know her,
he's like the flavor of the

09:37.643 --> 09:42.214
month. Besides,
I think you'd be surprised

09:42.247 --> 09:44.183
what teachers are capable of.

09:46.084 --> 09:47.619
Ladies.

09:47.653 --> 09:49.155
There she is.

09:49.421 --> 09:53.325
Gracing us with her presence,
the star of the show herself.

09:53.358 --> 09:57.128
Everybody bow down. Let's get
a fucking red carpet over here.

09:59.131 --> 10:00.800
Oh come on, I'm just kidding.

10:00.999 --> 10:03.035
You're gonna have
to get used to all the attention

10:03.068 --> 10:05.071
