it big on Broadway.

10:07.873 --> 10:11.143
Doin' alright? Looked like he
was giving you quite the earful.

10:11.176 --> 10:13.912
Yeah, I'm in
control of the situation.

10:13.945 --> 10:14.913
What does that even mean?

10:14.946 --> 10:17.182
It means I haven't
forgotten about yesterday.

10:17.215 --> 10:21.687
Barely made it to class,
Taylor. What took you so long?

10:21.720 --> 10:24.123
Yeah, I was
just taking some photos.

10:24.389 --> 10:25.933
I was talking
to the janitor in the hallway.

10:25.957 --> 10:26.925
Ew.

10:26.958 --> 10:27.892
You mean Drew?

10:27.926 --> 10:31.797
No, I mean ew. Barf.

10:31.830 --> 10:36.802
Guys, I've been thinking
and I feel like murder is in a

10:36.835 --> 10:39.005
janitor's skill set.

10:39.237 --> 10:43.074
Everyone find a good
stopping point and have a seat.

10:47.946 --> 10:50.750
By now I'm sure you've
all heard about Grace Fisher.

10:51.883 --> 10:54.687
A tragedy truly.

10:55.353 --> 10:58.357
She was a wonderful woman.

10:58.390 --> 11:00.660
We've all suffered a loss.

11:02.761 --> 11:05.197
I know this
is a tough situation.

11:05.230 --> 11:07.933
It's something we all never
thought we'd have to deal with.

11:09.868 --> 11:13.205
I'd be happy to
answer any questions,

11:14.773 --> 11:16.475
or maybe someone
has some comments

11:16.508 --> 11:19.144
that they'd like to share?

11:19.177 --> 11:21.347
Okay.

11:22.247 --> 11:25.217
Let's talk about
those midterm projects.

11:26.752 --> 11:31.390
The deadline
is quickly approaching.

11:37.095 --> 11:38.964
[CLASS BELL RINGING[

11:39.464 --> 11:40.999
Comin' Taylor?

11:41.032 --> 11:42.768
No, I'll meet you down there.

11:46.138 --> 11:48.407
Don't do anything I wouldn't do.

12:14.432 --> 12:17.202
The leading lady skipping class?

12:17.235 --> 12:19.037
