as your gal pals here.

18:22.634 --> 18:24.136
Oh my God, I'm looking

18:24.169 --> 18:25.704
forward to
our death scene tonight.

18:25.737 --> 18:27.573
Can you just fuck off?

18:29.307 --> 18:31.610
Okay, I'll fuck off.

18:37.382 --> 18:38.416
Really?

18:38.449 --> 18:39.417
