18:39.450 --> 18:42.187
Hardly. I would
rather suffocate to death then

18:42.220 --> 18:43.622
have to
lock lips with him again.

18:47.292 --> 18:50.428
Hey, can we
talk in the bathroom?

18:50.461 --> 18:52.297
Yeah.

19:00.538 --> 19:05.511
Alright, spill?
Taylor, what's going on?

19:07.845 --> 19:10.749
You still worrying
about that? It was just a joke.

19:10.782 --> 19:11.859
You went too far this time.

19:11.883 --> 19:15.353
